Subject: Capctha not appear
Description: I tried to access https://apps.pertamina.com/ivendor. The site asked to enter captcha to login, but the captcha did not appear. Due to urgent needs, I uninstalled the EPP client, after that the captcha appeared.
What_We_Know__c:
23-04 The customer tried to access a URL that asks to enter captcha to login, but the captcha is not loading.

24-04 Client: Windows 11 24H2, agent version: 6.2.3.1010

Server: EPP hosted, version: 5.9.4.1
Next_Steps__c:
23-04 We have requested additional details for a better understanding of the issue.

24-04 They informed us that  the EPP client was uninstalled so we recommend them to install the latest one 6.2.4.2 and retest the scenario to verify if the situation persist.

Also we have asked them to generate a set of logs.

29-04 We will schedule a remote session with the customer to check the errors.

02-05 In the meeting we have successfully fix the issue after we uninstall the client and remove the Stealthy DPI driver from the DPI module.
